(9, 8, 1, 1, 'bledixhindi', 'Covid-19 in Albania(essay)', '<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">At the moment the world is going through a global crisis. The events of recent years with the pandemic that spread with great speed. The events in Albania around Covid-19 are currently stabilized. 1 year ago Albania was hit hard by this pandemic. Lack of income made people get depressed.For almost 3 months we stayed in total quarantine. After 3 months the state had to open up and work had to continue normally. But with the invisible enemy on foot the only solution was a mask.</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">The summer season in Albania was characterized by a diverse tourism, this time it would be closed and few. The summer season made things worse and when autumn came the cases with Covid-19 exploded again. But after 6-7 months the state Albanians start vaccinating the population.</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">At the moment in Albania about 800 thousand people have been vaccinated. This is a good sign of recovery from this pandemic. On June 1 the rules for wearing the mask were suspended and we are seeing light at the end of the tunnel .</p><p><br/></p>', '185.89.159.80', 1633554493, 0);
