(23, 22, 1, 1, 'bledixhindi', 'Web browser-at me te perdorur dhe me te mire', '<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 0);\">Google Chrome:</span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 0);\"><a href=\"https://www.google.com/chrome/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/upload/image/20211007/1633555266750006.png\" alt=\"Google, chrome Free Icon of Social icons\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\"/></a></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">Google chrome eshte nje nga browser-at me te perdorur sot per sot ne bote.I ndertuar ne vitin 2008 nga kompania Google ai eshte nje browser shume i mire dhe shume i sigurt.Se pari kete browser mund ta perdornin vetem perdoruesat e windows por me kalimin e koheve ai i zhvilluar dhe mund te perdoret dhe ne Mac &amp; Linux.</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">FireFox:</span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><a href=\"https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/new/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/upload/image/20211007/1633555266196212.png\" alt=\"File:Firefox logo, 2019.svg - Wikimedia Commons\" width=\"85\" height=\"80\"/></a></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">Firefox nje web browser tjeter shume i perdorur gjere ne bote mund te renditet ne vendin e dyte per perdoruesat.FireFox eshte nje browser i cili mund te perdoret nga cdo lloje pajisje nga smartphone e deri tek PC.Mund te perdoret ne Windows,Mac &amp; Linux.</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\">Safari:</span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><a href=\"https://www.apple.com/safari/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/upload/image/20211007/1633555267712388.png\" alt=\"File:Safari browser logo.svg - Wikimedia Commons\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\"/></a></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">Safari nje web browser i cili eshte krijuar nga kompania Apple e cila eshte shume e famshme ne bote.Browserin safari e perdorin vetem pajisjet Apple.Numri i perdorueseve eshteÂ â 446 milion ne te gjithe boten.Ky eshte nje browser shume i sigurt dhe shume i mire per cdo pajisje jo vetem per apple.</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Brave:</span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"https://brave.com/download/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/upload/image/20211007/1633555269149805.png\" alt=\"The Logo For The Brave Browser - Brave Browser Logo Png, Transparent Png -  kindpng\" width=\"66\" height=\"80\"/></a></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">Brave nje web browserÂ  shume i mire i cili ka dale ne treg ne vitin 2019 eshte nje brawser qe po ben buje online .Brace ka shume permirsime disa prej tyre jane:Bllokimi i ads,Siguaria teper e lart,mundesia per te hyr ne nje tor browser etj.Sot per sot eshte nje nga browserat qe po rritet shume shpejt.</p><p><br/></p>', '185.89.159.80', 1633555299, 0),
