(36, 35, 1, 1, 'bledixhindi', 'Ankete mbi Familjen dhe Divorcin', '<p style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;\" src=\"/static/editor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_pdf.gif\"/><a style=\"font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;\" href=\"/upload/file/20211007/1633556217514401.pdf\" title=\"Ankete mbi Familjen dhe Divorcin  Andri Cepele.pdf\">Ankete mbi Familjen dhe Divorcin Â Andri Cepele.pdf</a></p><p><br/></p>', '185.89.159.80', 1633556238, 0),
(37, 36, 1, 1, 'bledixhindi', 'Genetically modified foods', '<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">Nowadays, technology has developed a lot. Humanity has created new methods for food production. With the growth of the population very soon we need more food. This leads us to think about better solutions. A solution to this problem is the genetic modification of foods. GMF is the change of DNA in the seed to produce more and to be produced faster. Many universities have developed biotechnology to enable the improvement of seeds to the maximum. GMF is in a way very efficient but it is also not very good. Genetic alteration of a species can lead to mutations that can damage human health. This is why University biologists have been working to modify the seeds so as not to cause harm to a human or a population.Bill gates an American businessman has created a company in the field of biotechnology. He thinks that with the development of technology genetic modification of seeds and will lead to a healthy use for humans.In my opinion humanity in 2030 will have better health because food will be improved and this will lead us to an increase in immunity to many viruses as well.</p><p><br/></p>', '185.89.159.80', 1633556269, 0),
